The airborne Jayde is able to avoid getting caught in the blast, but 
she's only provoked further by it.  "You're not getting away that 
easy!" she snarls as she dives after him - she knows he can't outrun 
her.  She fires several more shots at the speeding Tripredacus 
soldier.  "C'mon and fight, coward!"
